data.description: Your outdoor oasis is on the market and looking for a new buyer. Country living with fully fenced in 5 acres of land in a very private cul-de-sac in the highly sought after Hidden Springs neighborhood. This gorgeous French style built home by prestigious Salado home builder, Delton Stuckly is full of high end features. Beginning with the full marble backsplash covering the entire wall around the kitchen cabinets and vent hood. Gas cooktop, oversized Electrolux refrigerator and freezer, double oven and large kitchen island with a quartz countertop. The European white oak floors keep this home light, bright and feeling at home. You’ll love the additional square footage behind the hidden door in the master bedroom closet. Three French doors that open up to the backyard. With over 1,000 square feet of covered porch and patio entertaining space, including a rock built wood burning fireplace. There is a 8.1 kW solar power system that is owned and PAID IN FULL. This home is truly one of kind!
